explains: adj. 在东北的；东北方的；来自东北的

sentences.en: A moderate earthquake struck the northeastern United States early on Saturday.
sentences.cn: 美国东北部周六早晨遭遇了一次中等强度的地震。

sentences.en: Italy's industrial districts are concentrated in its north-central and northeastern regions.
sentences.cn: 意大利的工业区集中在该国中北部和东北部地区。

sentences.en: I just transferred from Northeastern State University near Chicago.
sentences.cn: 我刚从芝加哥附近的东北州立大学转过来。
